	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think I know how to get more bit depth. Vertical mirroring, black nametable 0, white nametable 1, use $2005 as if it were $4011. What this ends up doing is using the scroll to create pulse width modulation.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


