		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />When I was experimenting with it, I noticed using other color and brightness values it made louder or softer waveforms.  If someone were to experiment, they could create a look-up table of the loudest to softest or softest to loudest to create PCM waveforms.<br /><br />...It would also be prettier.

		

